nes (Continuous Quality Improvement). CQI formats are available at http://www.aiag.org/. For suppliers and sub-suppliers dealing with special processes according to AIAG, relevant CQI-guidelines shall be considered. For such processes yearly self-assessment shall be carried out in the whole supply chain. If the result shows findings of the type “Need for Immediate Action” or “Fail Findings”, the supplier shall inform Yazaki (Yazaki EMEA) immediately and provide an action plan. Upon Yazaki (Yazaki EMEA) request copies of the performed special process assessment cover sheet need to be provided within one day. "
