 receiving country/plant. Required documents for EU to EU: ▪ Invoice (only if shipping by air or sea) ▪ Packing list ▪ Shipping doc: AWB / CMR (Convention Marchandise Routier) / B of L Required documents for EU to non EU, EU to EU with transit non EU, non EU to EU, non EU to non EU ▪ Invoice (mandatory) ▪ Additional docs as per legal requirement of the concerned"
