 the shipment. For more details please to check EA-SC (Significant/Special Characteristic)-xx-M-001-A-03. Cost of Non-Compliance Documentation costs ▪ Export declaration / EX1 document: 50€ / shipment ▪ EUR1 / ATR: 50€ / shipment ▪ Web-Portal booking: 10€ / shipment Template"
